---
description: Rollout safety for Kubernetes and PostgreSQL changes
globs:
  - "**/*.go"
  - "**/*.sql"
  - "**/*.yml"
  - "**/*.yaml"
alwaysApply: true
---

## Rollout safety
- Assume rolling deployment, not instant replacement.
- New code must tolerate the migration window between old and new schema where applicable.
- Avoid schema changes that require disruptive locks during normal peak traffic unless explicitly planned.
- Do not merge database and application changes that are only safe if every pod updates simultaneously.
- Graceful shutdown, readiness, and database compatibility must all remain correct during rollout.